text: This synd thæs landes landgemære æt Halgastoke.
Ærest up on thone esc, Thonne ut on preosta lege an ane dic.
Thonene on thone ealdan herpath æt nitherstoce.
Thonne on thonne ford on livedic.
Thonne up on livedic oth holan broc.
Thonne up an holanbroc, Thonne on hlosbroc.
Of hlosbroce on withighege, Thonne on horsford.
Thonne up on horsford on fyres hylleford.
Thonne up on hlidan, Thonne ut on hunalege.
Thonne up on cric, Of cric on hunda troh.
Thonne on tymbercumb, Thonne on æsclege.
Of æsclege on faldhege, Thonne on readan weg.
Thonne up on stigele, Thonne an wibbelescumb up on æsc eft.
